Builder Upgrades Galore: Gourmet kitchen with double "convection" oven,  under cabinet lighting, granite countertops, pendant lighting,  kitchen cabinets with pullout drawers, 3 level music system,  interior privacy shutters , custom stair runner, storm door, fenced in backyard, master bath with upgraded heavy glass for the  shower and tall toilet upgrade.
